Description
-----------

iwmap is a simple script focused on activities of wardriving


To use iwmap
------------

   # cd path/to/iwmap
   # bash iwmap


Alternatively copy iwmap file on /usr/local/bin and run:

   # iwmap


Output
------

MACADDRESS 		 CH 	 FREQ 	 KEY 	 ENCR 	 ESSID
---------- 		 -- 	 ---- 	 --- 	 ---- 	 -----
